NK039(ti)026:1: // so dbal gri'i ral ngag man lo'i 'khor ti'i ma
NK039(ti)026:2: ti'i ma te mo lha ldan dpal gcig ma zhes
NK039(ti)026:4: na mo badz+ra d+ha ra ye /
NK039(ti)026:5: ma 'ongs bskal pa'i snyig ma yi dam lha mchog gang la yang /
NK039(ti)026:6: bsnyen bsgrub zin pa'i sngags pa yis //
NK039(ti)026:7: bden bral nyes byas sgrol ba'i las //
NK039(ti)026:9: gro ga shog bu gang srid steng tsakra mu khyud gsum bskor la /
NK039(ti)026:10: thabs 'khor dbus su dgra gzugs bkod //
NK039(ti)026:11: phyi rims rtsib brgyad b+h+yo brgyad dang //
NK039(ti)026:12: mchan brgyad dag la dgra bo'i //
NK039(ti)026:13: bla srog ngo bo r+n+rihdesa chog /
NK039(ti)026:15: thun sngags dang bcas rim bzhin no //
NK039(ti)026:16: yig mgo nang du bstan la mjug ma phyi //
NK039(ti)026:17: ming spel gsham bsgyur basngagasa byang ltar //
NK039(ti)026:18: yang gcig shes rab mo 'khor la //
NK039(ti)026:19: rtsib rtse dbal so nang du bstan //
NK039(ti)026:20: de steng b+h+yo brgyad mchan de la //
NK039(ti)026:21: nyes byas bla'am sa bon r+n+rih dbus su ling+ga mgo mjug ldog /
NK039(ti)026:22: yig mgo phyir bstan mjug la sogs //
NK039(ti)026:23: myu khyud dang bcas thabs 'khor bzhin //
NK039(ti)026:24: bris pa de nyid kha sbyor bsdom //
NK039(ti)026:26: dgos pa'i steng 'khor mu khyud gnyis //
NK039(ti)026:27: bskor dbus re ma ti yi sku //
NK039(ti)026:28: nag mo bong zhon dar nag gyon //
NK039(ti)026:29: ral gri thod khrag bsnams pa'o //
NK039(ti)026:30: yang na mngon rtog ltar gsal bri //
NK039(ti)026:31: sku yi thugs kar b+h+yo yig mtshan //
NK039(ti)026:32: zhes bkod phyi'i mu khyud la //
NK039(ti)026:33: yig mgo nang bstan sngags rnams bris //
NK039(ti)026:35: spyi dril sngags kyi bskor bar bya //
NK039(ti)026:36: yig 'go phyir bstan ming spel la //
NK039(ti)026:37: dam rdzas zag rdzas dri ma byug /
NK039(ti)026:38: man+dala steng bzhugs mdun bskyed ltar //
NK039(ti)026:40: 'bod rbad bsad gsum gsham du btag /
NK039(ti)026:41: man ngag ral gri'i dbal so yi //
NK039(ti)026:42: dgra las byas zin rlung 'khor bskor //
NK039(ti)026:43: dgra bo ma lus 'jogs par byed //
NK039(ti)026:44: ma cig lha mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)026:46: nyes med mi la bskor mi srid //
NK039(ti)026:47: ngan song la 'gro a tsa ma //
NK039(ti)026:48: ma cig lha mo re ma ti'i //
NK039(ti)026:49: bsad 'khor sngags byang nag po yi //
NK039(ti)026:51: 'bod rbad bsad gsum spyi dril ni /
NK039(ti)026:53: ma h+aa k+aa li re ma ti ma ma ru
NK039(ti)026:54: lu re ma ti ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yohdza
NK039(ti)026:55: dzah 'bod pa'o // ch+gee mo'i bla srog rnam par
NK039(ti)026:56: shes pa khug cig r+n+ri am gu sha dzahdzah +amo
NK039(ti)026:57: ru ru tsa tur a shug me /
NK039(ti)026:58: pra ti r+au tra kha shag rak+mo h'u /
NK039(ti)026:59: rak+sha tsit+ta sa ma ya ku ru kha tsit+ta nanah rbad pa'o //
NK039(ti)026:60: ch+gee mo'i yul du snang srid ma mo'i 'bum gyi dmag chos chos /
NK039(ti)026:61: rgyug rgyug dgra la nad yams phob phob sod sod /
NK039(ti)026:62: ru ru bam ro ru h'u /
NK039(ti)026:63: tish+tha ba to si rak+mo snying kha la rak+mo thun b+h+yohdza dzah thun sngags /
NK039(ti)026:65: ch+gee mo'i lus srog la nad rims sna tshogs thang thang phob la sod sod /
NK039(ti)026:66: ru lu re ma ti sa ma ya pra ma ha sti /
NK039(ti)026:67: pra ma rak+mo ru lu ru lu b+h+yo dza dzah
NK039(ti)026:68: kha rag te khem b+h+yoh kha le thun b+h+yoh thun
NK039(ti)026:70: h'u rak+mo r+n+ri sham ku ru thun rbad /
NK039(ti)026:71: rak+mo ar+ya dza dzah te khem kha le thun b+h+yo /
NK039(ti)026:73: sa ma ya dgra bo ch+gee mo'i srog rtsa chod
NK039(ti)026:74: r+n+ri ma ra ya rbad dzah 'bod rbad bsad gsum
NK039(ti)026:75: 'di yi bskor // ma cig dpal ldan lha mo la //
NK039(ti)026:76: bsnyen bsgrub phrin las byed pa dang //
NK039(ti)026:77: rlung 'khor drag po bskor ba'i dus //
NK039(ti)026:78: mchod bstod bskang bshag brtson na shis //
NK039(ti)026:79: lha mo 'khor bcas rgyu ba'i dus //
NK039(ti)026:80: gnam stong tshes brgyad bco lnga dang //
NK039(ti)026:81: nyi shu gnyis sogs nam phyed kun //
NK039(ti)026:82: 'jig rten ma lus khyab par nyul //
NK039(ti)026:83: rgyu dus phrin las ci byas myur //
NK039(ti)026:84: dus gtor gta' gtor grangs med bsngo //
NK039(ti)026:85: mngon spyod las brtson drag sngags bzlas //
NK039(ti)026:86: dgra bgegs ma lus 'joms par byed //
